                     <interp inst="t18220911-139-person1334" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Messrs. Lesters, who serve the prosecutor with wise; these bottles are marked the same as ours.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182209110069"></xptr>Cross-examined. Q. You mark all your wine so - A. All the old.</p>
